WEBVTT

00:00:59.375 --> 00:01:03.476
You know the old adage
"laughter is the best medicine?"

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:04.768
I hear that a lot.

00:01:04.792 --> 00:01:07.393
Now, at the same time,
there are studies to support it,

00:01:07.417 --> 00:01:08.684
but right now,

00:01:08.708 --> 00:01:11.684
I'd like to take you behind the nose
and go beyond the laughter

00:01:11.708 --> 00:01:14.518
and share a few things that I've seen
skating through ICUs.

00:01:14.542 --> 00:01:15.893
In my Heelys.

00:01:15.917 --> 00:01:17.167
Size 11.

00:01:17.917 --> 00:01:20.309
Because I take medical clowning

00:01:20.333 --> 00:01:23.476
very, very seriously.

00:01:23.500 --> 00:01:24.643
(Deflating sound)

00:01:24.667 --> 00:01:25.833
(Laughter)

00:01:26.667 --> 00:01:27.817
(Deflating sound)

00:01:28.951 --> 00:01:30.101
(Deflating sound)